}}'''Ḥmad Adɣrni''' (s [[tifinaɣ]] : ⵃⵎⴰⴷ ⴰⴷⵖⵉⵔⵏⵉ) , ilul ɣ wass n 5 mayu 1947 ɣ tawsit Ayt Ɛli ɣ yat ɣ tiwsitin n [[Ayt Baɛmran]] ɣ [[Lmɣrib]], immut ass n 19 uktubr 2020 ɣ [[Tiznit]]<ref>( fr ) Tamttant n Ḥmad_Adɣrni :http://article19.ma/accueil/archives/135958</ref>, iga amasatan, asrtan, amdyaz, amara d umɣnas n izrfan n [[Imaziɣen|imaziɣn]] ɣ [[Lmɣrib]].

Iɣṛa ɣ uswir amnzu ɣ usun "Taddart" , deffir maya ismd tiɣri nns ɣ usinag n [[Tiznit]], lliɣ ur ta idda s [[Tarudant|Trudant]], yumẓ aslkin n bakalurya ɣ usinan n usmuttg Yusf bn ɛli ɣ [[Mrrakc]], idda deffir maya s tsdawit n [[Fas]] yiwi-d gis turagt ɣ taẓlayt n uzrf. Idda ilmma s tsdawit n Muḥmmda 5 ɣ [[ⵔⵔⴱⴰⵟ|Rrbaṭ]], yumẓ gis turagt yaḍni ɣ taẓlayt n uzrf. Ikka-tt-in iga yan zɣ imɣnasn n  "Tamunt Tanamurt n Imzrawn n [[Lmɣrib]]" d illa ɣ umzaz n uzlmḍ.

Ɣ isggʷasn n 70, issnta taɣarast tazzulant zund umstan ɣ [[Sidi Sliman]] , deffir nns immutti s [[Rrbaṭ]].

== Tudrt nns ==
Ilul Ḥmad Adɣirni ɣ usggʷas n 1947 ɣ usun n taddart nna iwalan i tqqbilt n Ayt Ɛli ɣ [[Ayt Baɛmran|Ayt Baɛmṛan]] ,ikka tt inn babas iga aslmad ɣ tinml n Zzawit n taddart d umstan,iga u uḍwwaṛ n igʷrar n Sidi Ɛbdṛḥman ɣ tnila n [[Tiznit]], tagrawt n uglu iɣra n Dɣirni asslmd nns amnzu ɣ udɣar n tlalit nns, ismd taɣuṛi nns ɣ usinag n tznit aylliɣ immatti s win trudant, yumẓ tugga n lbak ɣ usinag n Bn Tacfin ɣ [[Mrrakc]], dffir n ma ann immattis tɣrmt n [[Fas]] lliɣ yumẓ turagt tasdawant ɣ tskla, issḍfṛ as yat turagt yaḍnin ɣ uslgn ɣ tsdawit n muḥmmad wiss smmus ɣ tɣrmt n ṛṛbaṭ,aylliɣ iswwuri d amstan ɣ ṛṛbaṭ nit zɣ asnti n ssbɛinat iga agmam ɣ twwuri tasrtant zɣ mẓẓiy nns ig ula agmam anmmassu ɣ tamunt n imzrawn n [[Lmɣrib]] iga igllin n Ḥmad adɣirni zɣ imqṛann n umussu amaiɣ d umɣar n imaziɣn akkʷ,yiws ɣ tinawin timzwura n tsdawit n unbdu ɣ ugadir,ig awd anmmassu ɣ tmagrawt tamaynut,ig zɣ inbdadn nna biddnin i uskkir n ukungṛi amaḍlan amaziɣ ,d umzday n usqqim anamur n izrfan n ufgan ɣ fyinna asggʷas n 1993,ig uwnni ann yan usrag n usussn n tmntilt tamaziɣt ɣ uswir amaḍlan,ig anbdad nna iskrn taswingmt n ukabaṛ adimuqṛati amaziɣ amaɣribi ɣ usggʷas n 2005 Ḥmad adɣirni ifld tugtt n warratn ɣ igr n tskla d umzruy d tsrtit ula asgd nna izdin d tmaziɣt,iskr awd taɣmmist n « amzday » d « tamaziɣt »,ittussan mass adɣirni dar imaiɣn akkʷ mas bdda inzzɣ f izrfan n imaziɣn ɣ mad izlin s tutlayt d usgd d tɣnsa s umata d inkraf isrtann kra gan.<ref>Amadalamazigh Press - Nuwanbir 2020/2970. Uṭṭun 238. [https://amadalamazigh.press.ma/archivesPDF/238.pdf <nowiki>[Ɣr ɣ wantirnit]</nowiki>]</ref>

