== Abrid n tɣnsa d tmsmunin ==
Abrid n tɣnsa n dda Ḥmad Adɣrni inta zɣ isggʷasen n 80 d umussu amaziɣ ɣ [[Lmɣrib]], idra ɣ tuwriwin n tsdawit n unbdu ɣ [[Agadir|Ugadir]] , d agd ɣ tmusmunt "Tamaynut<nowiki>''</nowiki>.

Ɣ isggʷasn n 90 ikka-tt-in iga anflus amatay n  UAU "Usqqim Anamur n uzdduy gr timsmunin timaziɣin n [[Lmɣrib]]".

=== Abrid asrtan ===
 
Isllwi dda Ḥmad Adɣrni amulli asrtan amaziɣ amzwaru ɣ [[Lmɣrib]] "Amulli Adimuqraṭi Amaziɣ" ɣ 2005, maka tgdlt tamawast n ugnsu tamɣrabit asggʷas n 2008.

=== Abrid anɣmas ===
Iga Ḥmad Adɣerni zɣ wi-nna isrsn tirsal n tɣmsa tasimant ɣ [[Lmɣrib]], tasɣunt " Tamaziɣt " lli isker tga tsɣunt tasimant tamzwarut ɣ tawunkt n [[Lmɣrib]]. Isllwi snat tsɣunin "Tamaziɣt " d "Amezday " s [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tutlayt tamaziɣt]] .
